    "heading": "Combine what's the same",
    "intro": "<p>You can only combine things of the <strong>same kind</strong>. Apples go with apples; the <em>x</em> terms go with <em>x</em> terms; plain numbers go with plain numbers. Just count how many of each.</p>",
    "examples": [
      "<strong>3 x's + 2 x's = 5 x's</strong>, written 3x + 2x = <strong>5x</strong>. (You added the counts: 3 + 2.)",
      "<strong>4 + 3x + 2</strong>: add the plain numbers 4 + 2 = 6, keep the 3x → <strong>3x + 6</strong>."
    ]
